data.description: Welcome Home! Seller is offer $5000 for Closing Costs or RATE buy down.  Well kept home boasting an enticing North/South facing orientation. Open great room w/ Shutters, tile in all the common areas (carpet in bedrooms). Split floorplan, Master Bath with double sinks, standing shower & walk in closet. Stunning Kitchen with load of cabinets, granite island, stainless appliances, pendant lights & subway backsplash. Nice backyard and patio with extended pavers. Home is nestled in the popular Meridian Community with unique amenities such as community garden, splash pad, community pool, themed parks including treehouse & firepits parks.
